operator Yasunobu Ogawa
submitter Yasunobu Ogawa (yogawa@nipr.ac.jp)
resources NI(16)
notes
We will conduct coordinated EISCAT-optical observations 
to investigate time-variable auroral phenomena such as 
flickering and pulsating aurorae. An optical instrument 
will be installed at S-Range in Kiruna.

We will run a sweep observational mode with beata pulse 
code.

